{"tid":1366401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"動漫電玩節開幕　中學生通宵排隊 有人預算花數千元買收藏品","createTime":"2019-07-26T02:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:45:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ebf9e053e1ecfa234ac31bc658dfeb49b2f9f8","tid":1366401,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"一年一度的動漫電玩節今日開幕，有動漫迷昨晚已在灣仔會展排隊等候入場。<br />\n<br />\n排頭位的張同學說，早前已花了一星期排隊領頭籌卡，昨晚7時來到會場外通宵排隊。他說排頭位是為了取得免費手機，亦希望購得動漫精品作收藏，預算花費5000元。<br />\n<br />\n另一名前排的殷先生亦同樣花了近一星期排隊領籌，更為此向公司請假。他同樣希望取得免費手機，及購買限量版模型，預算花費4000元。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470546-20190726.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470546-20190726.htm&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9x0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=8ff4d5f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470546-20190726.htm&h=da32c5ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470546-20190726.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ffa2bff8c8f2d2f88ac84b144128f6666ba46261","tid":1366401,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:00:35.000Z","msg":"咩電話  nokia?"},{"pid":"d6efe89c863d699691269720dd3574d7c9d79355","tid":1366401,"uid":48579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:02:17.000Z","msg":"廢宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f358210181b97e95ed13575e0f217c28d6dd6e04","tid":1366401,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:17:41.000Z","msg":"又到動物節"},{"pid":"956dfae5e89fc78f6555ac7b3211566f51927c6c","tid":1366401,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"4f0d78e64744df010169b0347145b179ee26c9cb","tid":1366401,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"本來買咗成套德國軍服可以攞去會展玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好衰唔衰呢個月先搞呢啲嘢，搞到我冇得攞去會展玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過可以拎去上環玩，重演歷史打共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269b47aa71edd9d9f2d6bf88aac771fd05bc7ee7","tid":1366401,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"956dfae5e89fc78f6555ac7b3211566f51927c6c","tid":1366401,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"0cec9d0064e73bf9385825f21c619ee78378b927","tid":1366401,"uid":156144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:54:23.000Z","msg":"冰火天魔公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdcc87a83a2473cea014398cbbab387519054a6","tid":1366401,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/comic-18_0I8Fn_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcomic-18_0I8Fn_1200x0.png&h=f36a9ab5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5ddb4a8be6e4bd6f078855d2d5e620ccd9edea7","tid":1366401,"uid":52760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:45:00.000Z","msg":"依班就真係社會垃圾"}]}